title: Justin Brooke - Flipping Burgers At Wendy’s To CEO Of Adskills

description:
Justin Brooke is the founder of IMScalable, digital ad agency that specializes in supplement companies, software companies and info publishing companies. 
 
Before Justin Brooke became an expert at ad buying, he was flipping burgers at Wendy's. He could barely afford to eat.
 
In this interview, we break down the best way to prove your offer online, and much more.
 
Show Notes: https://underdogempowerment.com/justin-brooke/
